简称，又被称为“点对点”。“对等”技术，是一种网络新技术，依赖网络中参与者的计算能力和带宽，而不是把依赖都聚集在较少的几台服务器上。P2P还是英文Point <br />\r\nto Point （点对点）的简称。它是下载术语，意思是在你自己下载的同时，自己的电脑还要继续做<a href="/view/23880.htm" target="_blank">主机</a>上传，这种下载方式，人越多速度越快但缺点是对硬盘损伤比较大（在写的同时还要读），还有对内存占用较多，影响整机速度。\r\n										</p>\r\n									</div>\r\n<br />\r\n									<div class="clear">\r\n									</div>\r\n								</div>\r\n							</div>\r\n<br />\r\n							<div id="catalog-0" class="text_dir nslog-area log-set-param" sizset="31" sizcache="0" data-nslog-type="1016" log-set-param="catalogshow" data-subindex="0">\r\n								<br />\r\n								<p>\r\n									目录\r\n								</p>\r\n<br />\r\n								<dl style="width:179px;padding-bottom:20px;visibility:hidden;" id="catalog-holder-0" class="holder1" sizset="31" sizcache="0">\r\n									<br />\r\n									<dd sizset="31" sizcache="0">\r\n										<a class="nslog:1274" href="#1" name="STAT_ONCLICK_UNSUBMIT_CATALOG">影响</a><br />\r\n									</dd>\r\n									<dd sizset="32" sizcache="0">\r\n										<a class="nslog:1274" href="#2" name="STAT_ONCLICK_UNSUBMIT_CATALOG">发展历程</a><br />\r\n										<ol style="display:none;" sizset="33" sizcache="0">\r\n											<br />\r\n											<li sizset="33" sizcache="0">\r\n												<a href="#2_1">发展历程</a><br />\r\n											</li>\r\n											<li sizset="34" sizcache="0">\r\n												<a href="#2_2">P2P技术软件</a> \r\n											</li>\r\n										</ol>\r\n<br />\r\n									</dd>\r\n									<dd sizset="35" sizcache="0">\r\n										<a class="nslog:1274" href="#3" name="STAT_ONCLICK_UNSUBMIT_CATALOG">定义</a><br />\r\n									</dd>\r\n									<dd sizset="36" sizcache="0">\r\n										<a class="nslog:1274" href="#4" name="STAT_ONCLICK_UNSUBMIT_CATALOG">分类</a><br />\r\n										<ol style="display:none;" sizset="37" sizcache="0">\r\n											<br />\r\n											<li sizset="37" sizcache="0">\r\n												<a href="#4_1">依中央化程度</a><br />\r\n											</li>\r\n											<li sizset="38" sizcache="0">\r\n												<a href="#4_2">纯P2P：</a><